    "k-NN follows (10 times on 38), with k set at 31 (8 times) and 39 (twice) and, mostly, with numeric input.",
    "Then, random forest wins 7 times on 38, always when the input is considered as a score.",
    "Logistic regression never outperforms the other algorithms.",
    "Once the best prediction algorithm had been determined and implemented, it was tested on a real case.",
    "As said, the test consisted in comparing the support tools and strategies that a sample of 43 dyslexic students found useful or useless, after trying them in studying, with the prediction output by the algorithm when fed with the issues experienced by the students during their career."
